== INKSCAPE ==

== align object to page ==

::select object::
shift + ctrl + a - align
relative to:  page
center on vertical axis
center on horizontal axis

== workspace ==

shift + ctrl + f - fill
shift + ctrl + l - layers
shift + ctrl + w - swatches
shift + ctrl + a - align
object > rows and columns

== hotkeys ==

s - select
n - node
w - tweak
z - zoom
r - rectangle
x - 3D
e - elipse
* - star
i - spiral
p - pencil
b - bezier curve
c - calligraphy
t - text
a - spray
b - big eraser
u - paint tool
g - gradient
d - eye dropper
o - diagram connector

ctrl + a - select all
ctrl + z - undo
ctrl + shift + z - redo
+ - zoom in
- - zoom out
# - grid
drag from ruler - guide
ctrl + g - group
ctrl + u - ungroup
ctrl + drag - increment
shift + drag - draw from center
ctrl + click - change color
shift + click perspective - depth
ctrl + alt + drag - perfect circle
s + <> - scale
s + [] - rotate